♪ Maggie, did we mention,
as our newest friend ♪

33:55.880 --> 33:58.080
♪ You gotta pay for
all the food this year ♪

33:58.080 --> 33:59.920
-It's tradition, Maggie.
-No!

33:59.920 --> 34:04.500
♪ You will get a sentimental
feeling when you see ♪

34:05.460 --> 34:08.380
♪ Gary in his
Christmas sweater ♪

34:08.380 --> 34:10.830
