wears it better ♪

34:10.830 --> 34:12.330
In your dreams.

34:12.330 --> 34:13.960
♪ Rockin' around
the Dixons' tree ♪

34:13.960 --> 34:16.040
♪ At Delilah's party hop ♪

34:16.040 --> 34:17.750
Ooh!

34:17.750 --> 34:20.210
♪ Mistletoe weirdly
dangling from

