to vacate this house.

34:39.460 --> 34:41.420
No, there's got
to be a mistake.

34:41.420 --> 34:43.580
My husband and I paid off
this house years ago.

34:43.580 --> 34:45.670
Maybe you should
talk to him about that.

34:59.210 --> 35:00.330
Sophie:
Oh, that is so awesome.

35:00.330 --> 35:01.920
Eddie: Sending this one out
to all you --

35:01.920 --> 35:04.330
Regina:

35:04.330 --> 35:06.080
Hey.

35:06.080 --> 35:07.210
Hey.

35:07.210 --> 35:08.210
Is everything okay?

35:08.210 --> 35:09.080
Yes. Yes.

35:09.080 --> 35:10.460
Eddie: Oh, yeah.

35:10.460 --> 35:12.580
Regina, what you got for me?
Come on.

35:12.580 --> 35:13.830
I should get her home.

35:13.830 --> 35:15.830
No. No, I don't want
to interrupt the party.

35:15.830 --> 35:17.120
I'm just gonna call a ride.

35:18.580 --> 35:20.960
You know I'm your ride.

35:20.960 --> 35:23.420
Thank you for being here
with all of us today.

35:23.420 --> 35:26.250
Oh, thank you
for inviting me.

35:26.250 --> 35:28.040
Oh, almost forgot
my new scarf.

35:30.040 --> 35:33.420
Oh, I got a scarf just like that
for Ashley last Christmas.

35:35.080 --> 35:38.120
Oh. Must be
a very popular scarf.

35:38.120 --> 35:40.080
Well, let's
get you home, huh?

35:40.080 --> 35:40.830
Mm-hmm.
All right.

35:45.790 --> 35:47.420
Ashley, really?

35:47.420 --> 35:49.120
Here we go.

35:49.120 --> 35:50.250
Mm.

35:50.250 --> 35:51.330
I knew it.
See, I knew it.

35:51.330 --> 35:53.120
I knew that you couldn't
just be friends.

35:53.120 --> 35:54.500
Oh, no,
I can be your friend.

35:54.500 --> 35:55.920
