I'm not upset.

35:55.920 --> 35:57.290
Of course you're upset.

35:57.290 --> 35:58.710
No, I'm not.
I'm not upset.

35:58.710 --> 35:59.830
Of course you're upset.
How could you not be upset?

35:59.830 --> 36:01.460
I slept with someone.

36:01.460 --> 36:02.380
I am aware.

36:02.380 --> 36:03.330
And you're upset.

36:04.420 --> 36:07.290
Please don't tell me
how I feel right now.

36:07.290 --> 36:09.500
You have no idea
what I am feeling.

36:09.500 --> 36:10.830
Okay, then, how about --
how about this?

36:10.830 --> 36:12.540
How about I tell you
how I'm feeling?

36:12.540 --> 36:15.080
You want to know why
I had sex with Ashley?

36:15.080 --> 36:16.670
Oh, God,
I don't know, Gary.

36:16.670 --> 36:18.080
Why?

36:18.080 --> 36:20.000
Because I'm
in love with you.

36:31.620 --> 36:33.670
Oh, no.

36:33.670 --> 36:36.040
Ohh, no.

36:37.670 --> 36:39.250
Ugh.

36:39.250 --> 36:40.380
I'm so sorry.

36:40.380 --> 36:42.790
This is your new car.

36:46.670 --> 36:48.750
Ugh.

36:57.830 --> 36:59.830
Oh, my God.

37:02.330 --> 37:03.710
Oh.

37:04.290 --> 37:06.330
Oh, my God.
