37:24.120 --> 37:26.290
This is your car,
your gas.

37:26.290 --> 37:28.540
It's literally
the least I could do.

37:28.540 --> 37:31.670
Now, listen, you are going
to crush this, okay?

37:31.670 --> 37:32.790
Put it on Instagram.

37:32.790 --> 37:34.750
I'll even consider
getting an account.

37:34.750 --> 37:36.670
Thanks for everything.

37:36.670 --> 37:38.880
Also...

37:38.880 --> 37:39.750
These people...

37:43.420 --> 37:45.080
I said these people.

37:45.080 --> 37:46.000
Whoa.
What, what, what, what?

37:46.000 --> 37:47.040
-Hey!
-Us, comin' out?

37:47.040 --> 37:48.380
-Hey!
-What?

37:48.380 --> 37:50.710
Yeah, go get some love.
Dude.

37:50.710 --> 37:53.540
Last chance, okay?
Last chance.

37:53.540 --> 37:55.540
Manager, okay?

37:55.540 --> 37:57.460
I am the smart choice.
Think about it.

37:57.460 --> 38:00.040
Yeah. We have a manger.
His name is Jeffrey.

38:00.040 --> 38:02.120
Jeffrey's got you on a bus.
I'd have had you on a jet.

38:02.120 --> 38:03.040
Safe travels, man.

38:03.040 --> 38:06.000
♪ There's a battle ahead ♪

38:06.000 --> 38:08.460
♪ Many battles are lost ♪

38:08.460 --> 38:10.120
♪ But you'll never see
the end of the road ♪

38:10.120 --> 38:11.620
♪ While you're traveling ♪

38:11.620 --> 38:14.790
I want a concert
T-shirt, okay?
Done.

38:14.790 --> 38:16.500
♪ Hey now, hey now ♪
Not one of yours.
The Lumineers.

38:17.500 --> 38:18.290
Okay, thank you.

38:19.330 --> 38:20.960
♪ Don't dream it's over ♪

