I love you.

39:27.580 --> 39:29.290
I'm blessed to have you
in my life, Gina.

39:29.290 --> 39:30.540
Mm-hmm.

39:30.540 --> 39:32.620
And all I want
for Christmas is us.

39:35.210 --> 39:38.500
But before I can
get back to us,

39:38.500 --> 39:41.710
I got to get back to me,
Gina.

39:41.710 --> 39:47.250
And I will. I will.

39:47.250 --> 39:49.500
I want to get off
the meds, Gina.

39:51.960 --> 39:55.040
♪ Now I'm walking again ♪

39:55.040 --> 39:57.670
♪ To the beat of a drum ♪

39:57.670 --> 40:01.790
♪ And I'm counting the steps
